subject: Breeders' Cup (Horse Race)
Curlin (Race Horse)
Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Henrythenavigator split through a logjam in midpack and Raven’s Pass swung outside Curlin and took dead aim on the finish line winning the race in 1:59.27.
